                        <sli class="- topic/sli " xtrc="sli:2;29:30" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/patscully/Dropbox/Current%20Working%20Clients/Information%20Designs%20&amp;%20Development/project_2_ps/workspace/publications/deployment_and_configuration_guide/topics/references/stack-provisioning_prerequisites.dita">– The gateway IP address to and from the application stack IP address on port 8765 and 5432</sli>
